 Empty soda cans and bottles of all liquid. 
 Empty food containers before recycling them. 
 Compost all food scraps.
https://bit.ly/2AWkaEV

text:
The trash patch in the Pacific is much bigger than we thought - but you can help stop it from getting bigger.
 Bring your own resusable cup, mug & water bottle
 Skip single-use plastic such as straws & cups
 Avoid heavily packaged foods
https://n.pr/2DQ2Zms
